VASBURG 10/20/40/80
Atorvastatin Tablets 10 mg/20 mg/40 mg/80 mg

INN: Atorvastatin

Description:
Atorvastatin is a synthetic lipid-lowering agent. Atorvastatin calcium is a selective, competitive inhibitor of HMG-CoA reductase, the rate-limiting enzyme that converts 3-hydroxy-3-methylglutaryl-coenzyme A to mevalonate, a precursor of sterols, including cholesterol.

